      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always kept in the garage, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
