    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S54 powertrain. Featuring a high-revving 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies, this unit offers instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a complete Double VANOS rebuild and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut, riding on a refreshed suspension geometry that preserves its legendary handling characteristics. Meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, the finish and interior upholstery are in showroom state. A rare, collector-grade example for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
