    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive care. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been protected with a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept and exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is remarkably tidy. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive excellence, perfect for a discerning collector or an enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
